digiKam 4.4.0 - Release date: 2014-10-12

*****************************************************************************************************
NEW FEATURES:

General     : Navigate between pictures using PageUp/PageDown is now possible while editing properties through captions/tags sidebar.
General     : New keyboard shortcuts to improve usability while photo review (as to switch focus on text edit widget, or to toogle tags view).
General     : New keyboard shortcut to switch on/off color managed view for thumbnails and preview.

AlbumGUI    : Album preview can be displayed in tooltip.

SlideShow   : Labels and Tags keyboard shortcuts can be used while slideshow.
SlideShow   : Support multi-monitors computer.

PiwigoExport: Allow to upload videos (OGG, MP4 and WEBM) if the Piwigo server accept them.
PiwigoExport: Remove the support of old Piwigo API (version < 2.4).

